Salaries after 10 years for graduates of three different universities

Data for Example 10.7

Format

A data frame with 51 observations on the following 6 variables.

UnivB
a numeric vector
UnivC
a numeric vector
salary
a numeric vector
university
a numeric vector
ranks
a numeric vector
